Package io.github.goodees.ese.core.matching

Utilities for type-based branch switching.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SyncRequestHandler.Handler<T,U>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RequestHandler
    Special kind of type switch, which maps to CompletionStage<RS> for many different subclasses of Request<RS>, all with different response types.
    RequestHandler.Builder
    Builder for request handler.
    SyncRequestHandler
    Special kind of type switch, to support Request<RS> for synchronous entities (that may throw checked exceptions).
    SyncRequestHandler.Builder
    Builder for request handler.
    TypeSwitch
    Typesafe and boilerplate-free instance matching.
    TypeSwitch.Builder  
    TypeSwitchExpression<E>
    Typesafe and boilerplate-free instance matching that returns a value.
    TypeSwitchExpression.Builder<E>
